For a CRM targeting health clinics, insurance agencies, real estate, and SMB sales teams (similar to what you've discussed for your AI chatbot business), I'd prioritize WhatsApp + Email + Calendar + Calling + AI + E-signature + Payments first, because those integrations deliver the highest customer value and fastest ROI.
